data.description: Well kept Kalaheo home  offers an assumable 2.99% VA loan!  Main home has 3 bedrms/2 bths & 1 bedrm/1 bth permitted additional dwelling w/laundry facilities. Private tropical paradise on 21,000 sqft. rim lot w/great views of Mt Kahili Owner occupied main home & ADU are each on 1 level.  Relax or party in the permitted 8 person  jacuzzi while  enjoying  the fire pit on it’s own thick slab under a stylish structure while taking in the mountain views. The 18 panel photovoltaic w/ tesla battery backup installed by Nathan Woods General contractor. Lots of hot water with the 2 solar water panels and a 120 gallon hot water heater helps to significantly reduces the electric bills & comes with a 47 to 49 yr warranty.  Split AC/heater in the living room has 1 more free maintenance service appointment.  Large storage/laundry room plumbed for additional bath/shower closet including new toilet & sink, plus a cute detached 8ft x 12ft storage building.  Located on the sunnier side of Kalaheo in a quaint neighborhood on a quiet cul-de-sac w/long time owners. Within easy walking distance to Kukuiolono Golf Course at the golf restaurant.  This property is owner loved!  Main Home: Granite counters tops, Koa trimmed cabinets, Red Oak wood flooring in the living area, large porcelain tile floors in the bedrm & baths, 2 sky lights w/blinds, Quality vinyl louvers window treatments, Vinyl windows open in to clean, Putting green zoysia grass, Stainless steel electric 2 yr old GE double door refrigerator, Stainless steel 2 yr old double oven convection oven w/elect stove top, 5 yr comp roof, Nice paint job in & out. ADU: Travertine stone Italian tile floors in the bedrm & bths, Granite counter tops, New Samsung refrigerator.   Extensive drainage system. Enjoy mature citrus and tropical fruit trees.  The iron wood tree & variety of hibiscus hedge on 3 sides provides privacy.  Chain link fence for the dogs and a home security system.
